divs: Sighting DetailsI saw 2 bright yellow white rod shaped objects that looked like the capital letter I. They were below broken up cloud cover coming from the West. I estmate the length @ about 1 inch. I thought they were planes that were going to crash because 1 was stationary & the second was head straight toward it. When the second got very close the first moved slightly East and vanished then the second did the same. At the exact same I saw another object just like the first 2 approaching from the West at a higher rate of speed and it disappeared where the other 2 had gone. A few seconds later another one came from the West and even faster vanished. I was in my backyard. I have lived here27 years @ go outside often @ night to take my dog outside. I was awe struck, couldn't believe what I'd seen, called my friends, the sheriff's dept, emailed the local news snd now you. I am fristrated and want to know what I saw was real. Was it an explainable phenomenon? I don't care if anyone believes me because I know what I saw. Please let me know what you think.
